## Validation Helpers

### validates_associated

```ruby
class Article < ApplicationRecord
  has_many :comments
  validates_associated :comments
  # Validates each associated comment
end
```

### validates_each

```ruby
class User < ApplicationRecord
  validates_each :email, :backup_email do |record, attr, value|
    if value.present? && value.include?('spam')
      record.errors.add(attr, 'cannot contain spam')
    end
  end
end
```

